      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid choice for someone looking for reliable transportation on a budget. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor dings on the passenger side, and some fading on the clear coat. Inside, the cabin is functional but shows wear on the driver\u2019s seat upholstery and some staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, though it may soon require routine maintenance such as new brake pads and a suspension check to return it to peak smoothness. It\u2019s an honest car that has been used daily and is priced to reflect its current state.",
