    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve spent more weekends polishing this beauty than I care to admit, and it honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been garaged since day one and drives like an absolute dream\u2014smooth, responsive, and it turns heads at every single corner. There might be a tiny, barely-visible speck on the bumper from a stray pebble, but that just shows it's been loved and enjoyed! I'm only letting it go to make some room in the driveway, and I'd really love for it to go to someone who will cherish it as much as I have. Come on by, let's grab a coffee, and you can see for yourself just how special this ride is!",
      "price": 43500.0,
