      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered here is a meticulously sorted example of precision engineering, boasting a blueprinted powertrain that delivers a perfectly linear torque curve. This vehicle features a recalibrated ECU mapped for optimized stoichiometric efficiency and a high-capacity thermal management system to ensure peak performance under any load. The chassis has been enhanced with high-durometer bushings and a precision-aligned subframe, resulting in zero lash and surgical turn-in response. Every synchromesh remains crisp, and the limited-slip differential has been freshly shimmed for maximum bite. This isn't just a showroom piece; it is a mechanically superior specimen maintained to a standard that exceeds OEM requirements. For the buyer who demands a car that performs as sharply as it looks, this is the definitive choice.",
      "price": 48500.0,
